  <section>
    <div class="wrap">
      <header>
        <h1>Counseling Services</h1>
      </header>
      
      <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
        <p style="color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 16px;">
          Rates vary by clinician and telehealth availability. We also offer Open Path reduced-rate options. 
          See our <a href="/services/reduced-rate">Reduced Rate page</a> for more details.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
        <h3>Our Approach</h3>
        <p style="color: var(--muted);">
          We provide individual, couples, and family counseling services tailored to your unique needs. 
          Our team of licensed professionals uses evidence-based approaches including CBT, ACT, DBT, EMDR, and more.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div style="margin-top: 24px;">
        <a href="/services/overview" class="btn tertiary">‚Üê Back to Services</a>
